.TH snmpm 3 "snmp 5.20.1" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
snmpm \- Interface functions to the SNMP toolkit manager

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The module \fIsnmpm\fR contains interface functions to the SNMP manager.

