.PP
Restart the indicated process (\fIWhat\fR). Note that its not without risk to restart a process, and should therefore be used with care.


.RE
.B
\fBset_log_type(NewType) -> {ok, OldType} | {error, Reason}\fR
\fB                      when\fR
\fB                          NewType :: snmp:atl_type(),\fR
\fB                          OldType :: snmp:atl_type(),\fR
\fB                          Reason :: term().\fR

.br
.RS
